This paper combines reinforcement learning with one-shot learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper also deals with image classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The use of a recurrent neural network suggests a focus on deep learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves decision-making, which is a key aspect of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of reinforcement learning suggests a focus on robotics (cs.RO), and the use of neural networks suggests a focus on neural engineering (cs.NE).
